01:15:28.655 --> 01:15:33.388
Nancy, I'm gonna need the keys
to your car, and I want you to call the police.

01:15:33.494 --> 01:15:36.395
<i>Not the Secret Service.</i>
<i>The police. Tell 'em about the Cadillac.</i>

01:15:36.497 --> 01:15:39.466
- Okay.
- Thanks.

01:16:39.092 --> 01:16:42.323
<i>I was waiting there maybe three hours.</i>
<i>Nobody showed up.</i>

01:16:42.429 --> 01:16:44.659
<i>I didn't want</i>
<i>to stay there all day.</i>

01:16:44.765 --> 01:16:47.928
She didn't go nowhere.
