01:20:14.675 --> 01:20:17.974
Listen. This is not enough
to take back to Overbrook and clear you.

01:20:18.078 --> 01:20:20.546
<i>Dave, I don't know</i>
<i>what to tell you.</i>

01:20:20.647 --> 01:20:24.413
They're gonna hit him
in Toronto, G8 Summit.

01:20:24.518 --> 01:20:27.351
Pete. Pete?

01:20:30.323 --> 01:20:33.781
Sarah?

01:20:33.894 --> 01:20:36.522
Listen, I'm leaving
for Toronto tonight.

