01:21:22.242 --> 01:21:24.210
I love you.

01:21:30.317 --> 01:21:32.877
I want you to get the crime scene unit
out here immediately.

01:21:32.986 --> 01:21:35.887
Rip this place apart. Find me something now.

01:21:35.989 --> 01:21:37.923
- This is Agent Breckinridge.
- Agent Breckinridge?

01:21:38.024 --> 01:21:41.425
Sarah Ballentine.

01:21:43.029 --> 01:21:44.997
<i>Come in.</i>

01:21:46.933 --> 01:21:50.300
<i>Excuse me, ma'am.</i>

01:21:50.403 --> 01:21:52.234
Thanks, Tom.

01:21:54.407 --> 01:21:57.069
- Could I offer you a drink?
- No, thank you, ma'am.

01:21:59.479 --> 01:22:01.606
You know, most women
don't like whiskey...

01:22:01.715 --> 01:22:05.446
but my mama was from Tennessee.

01:22:09.456 --> 01:22:12.016
Pete Garrison and I are having an affair.

01:22:15.295 --> 01:22:19.197
Please have a seat.
And... that's for you.

01:22:20.734 --> 01:22:23.498
You know, I don't know
all the evidence you have against him...

01:22:23.603 --> 01:22:26.800
but I do know why he failed
the lie detector test.

01:22:26.907 --> 01:22:32.038
And I know why he was
in that coffee shop looking for someone.

01:23:16.156 --> 01:23:20.149
Hello. U.S. Secret Service
up for the G8.

01:23:20.260 --> 01:23:22.820
I got a priority item
for the duty officer over at the lab.

01:23:22.929 --> 01:23:26.922
- That'll be that direction on the eighth floor.
- Thank you.

01:23:27.033 --> 01:23:29.524
Sign the log, please.

01:23:36.076 --> 01:23:40.012
I need any prints that
you can find off this cup.

01:23:40.113 --> 01:23:42.604
- Okay.
- Thank you very much.

01:23:44.851 --> 01:23:46.944
See you in about 12 minutes.

01:24:05.138 --> 01:24:07.698
<i>Sweeps two and three now complete.</i>

01:24:47.414 --> 01:24:49.882
