with access to the president.

01:27:13.893 --> 01:27:16.020
Yours was the only one
that showed deception.

01:27:16.129 --> 01:27:19.257
We need to figure out
how the real traitor passed the test.

01:27:19.365 --> 01:27:20.992
Montrose had the list.

