You know I never guaranteed you success.

01:27:26.806 --> 01:27:28.706
Security's tighter than it's ever been.

01:27:28.808 --> 01:27:32.608
Routes, modes of transport,
they're all random now.

01:27:32.712 --> 01:27:35.010
<i>Yeah, but not random</i>
<i>to you, William.</i>

01:27:35.115 --> 01:27:40.644
I mean, if you wanted him on that helicopter
at Camp David, you could have put him there.

01:27:42.522 --> 01:27:45.616
<i>Now, you've been playing us</i>
<i>since the beginning.</i>

01:27:45.725 --> 01:27:48.421
<i>All right. Fair enough.</i>

01:27:48.528 --> 01:27:51.361
That's not gonna work anymore.

01:27:51.464 --> 01:27:54.763
- You did make a deal.
- Yeah.

01:27:54.868 --> 01:27:57.837
Twenty years ago with the K.G.B.,
which doesn't even exist anymore.

01:27:57.937 --> 01:28:00.497
Do you want out, William?

01:28:06.713 --> 01:28:09.978
Then give me... the president.

01:28:10.083 --> 01:28:12.176
<i>Just like you agreed.</i>

01:28:12.285 --> 01:28:14.253
No.

01:28:16.389 --> 01:28:18.357
I don't care.

01:28:19.492 --> 01:28:21.483
Expose me.

01:28:21.594 --> 01:28:25.428
I don't care if I spend the rest
of my life in prison for treason.

01:28:25.532 --> 01:28:28.126
I don't care if you kill me.

01:28:30.803 --> 01:28:34.364
- Here you go.
- Have a pint.

01:28:38.411 --> 01:28:41.209
Oh. Thank you.

01:28:42.549 --> 01:28:45.985
William...

01:28:46.085 --> 01:28:49.054
if you don't do this,
we're not gonna kill you.

01:28:56.963 --> 01:28:59.727
We are going to kill her.

01:29:03.803 --> 01:29:06.067
And we're gonna kill her.

01:29:08.107 --> 01:29:10.075
And then we're gonna kill her.

01:29:20.887 --> 01:29:23.879
<i>Yes, William, the K.G.B. 's gone.</i>

01:29:23.990 --> 01:29:26.458
<i>But we're still here.</i>

01:29:29.295 --> 01:29:31.855
<i>William, it's all right.</i>

01:29:31.965 --> 01:29:34.525
You do have a way out.

01:29:34.634 --> 01:29:36.602
But only one.

01:29:44.043 --> 01:29:47.069
When he finishes his speech,
you take him on the primary route...

01:29:47.180 --> 01:29:49.876
to the "B" motorcade
under the plaza...

