<i> Be advised,</i>
<i>they just allowed two armed credentialed...</i>

01:32:30.476 --> 01:32:32.808
<i>American agents into the three perimeter</i>
<i>from checkpoint 386.</i>

01:32:32.912 --> 01:32:36.905
<i> Be advised,</i>
<i>suspect Garrison has just been let through-</i>

