01:33:39.145 --> 01:33:42.444
He wanted me to tell you
that Montrose is the mole.

01:33:44.517 --> 01:33:49.113
<i> But I strongly believe</i>
<i>that we can protect our vital interests...</i>

01:33:49.222 --> 01:33:51.816
