01:33:51.924 --> 01:33:54.620
Get your hands in the air!

01:33:54.727 --> 01:33:58.288
- Put that down!
- Pete Garrison is not the mole!

01:33:58.397 --> 01:34:00.991
<i>- You are a Do Not Admit!</i>
- But at the same time-

01:34:01.100 --> 01:34:04.501
- Mr. President.
<i>- Listen to me!</i>

01:34:04.604 --> 01:34:07.334
<i>Do not let him</i>
<i>move the president!</i>

01:34:07.440 --> 01:34:09.408
This way, Mr. President.

01:34:09.509 --> 01:34:12.239
- Do not let Montrose move the president!
- Montrose, he's getting away!

01:34:12.345 --> 01:34:15.212
Crystal. Crystal is the password.

01:34:18.417 --> 01:34:21.215
We need your help.
Tom, get the first lady to the motorcade.

01:34:25.658 --> 01:34:28.149
It's all right.

01:34:28.261 --> 01:34:32.254
- Freeze!
- Password is Crystal.
Where'd Montrose take the president?

01:34:32.365 --> 01:34:35.562
- Motorcade "B."
- Stay with me, ma'am.

01:34:39.672 --> 01:34:41.731
This way.

01:34:46.045 --> 01:34:49.572
- It's just this way, ma'am.
- Tom, where are we going?

01:34:49.682 --> 01:34:52.674
We're going to motorcade "C," ma'am.

01:34:56.556 --> 01:34:59.024
That's a hell of a way
to leave the G8.

01:34:59.125 --> 01:35:02.959
<i>What is going on</i>
<i>with these goddamn radios?</i>

01:35:11.037 --> 01:35:13.733
Go in twos.

01:35:18.077 --> 01:35:21.740
What's next, boss?
What's the next move?

01:35:21.847 --> 01:35:24.645
<i>- What's next?</i>
- Bill?

01:35:24.750 --> 01:35:27.810
Hold the corridor.
Push 'em back.

01:35:38.564 --> 01:35:40.896
Crystal!

01:35:43.636 --> 01:35:47.231
<i> Pete, we're cut off</i>
<i>from the "B" motorcade.</i>

01:36:12.131 --> 01:36:15.032
You okay?

01:36:15.134 --> 01:36:17.034
- I think so.
- Turn off your locator.

01:36:17.136 --> 01:36:19.127
What?

01:36:19.238 --> 01:36:23.106
Your locator, turn it off. That's how
they know where we are. They're tracking us.

01:36:23.209 --> 01:36:27.111
How do you-
How do you know?

01:36:30.249 --> 01:36:33.878
Oh, no, Bill. Oh, God.

01:36:52.905 --> 01:36:55.601
<i>Montrose was-</i>

01:37:20.866 --> 01:37:23.733
<i>Pete. Pete.</i>

01:37:23.836 --> 01:37:26.566
My family. My family. Pete!

01:37:31.577 --> 01:37:34.045
Mr. President,
you're gonna have to trust us.

01:37:34.146 --> 01:37:36.671
<i>We're gonna get you</i>
<i>up top to an evac car.</i>

01:37:56.469 --> 01:37:59.495
Shooter's at 11:00.
I'll go high. You go low. You ready?

01:37:59.605 --> 01:38:01.436
- Yeah.
<i>- Go.</i>

01:38:10.716 --> 01:38:13.776
Get the president upstairs.
We'll cover you from here.

01:38:30.436 --> 01:38:33.428
This way, ma'am.
As quick as you can.

01:38:33.539 --> 01:38:36.064
Yes. Garrison.

01:38:36.175 --> 01:38:39.110
<i>Need a hard car for</i>
<i>the president at southwest two.</i>

01:38:39.211 --> 01:38:41.441
Coming to you, Pete.
Go. Go! Go, go!

01:38:41.547 --> 01:38:43.947
<i>Southwest stairs.</i>
<i>Let's go get 'em!</i>

01:38:44.049 --> 01:38:46.244
All right, we're gonna
get you out of here.

01:39:39.638 --> 01:39:43.665
<i>Give me a perimeter</i>
<i>10 meters, 360 degrees!</i>

01:39:57.489 --> 01:39:59.650
<i>President's hard car!</i>
<i>Let's get him in!</i>

01:39:59.758 --> 01:40:03.558
Pete, I got him.
Mr. President, you're with me.

01:40:21.881 --> 01:40:24.247
<i>The president is away!</i>

01:40:31.056 --> 01:40:32.853
Go, go, go, go!

01:40:36.729 --> 01:40:40.631
Oh, my God!
Oh, my God.

01:40:46.071 --> 01:40:48.904
<i>- Secure the first lady!</i>
<i>- We need a hard car, now!</i>

01:41:18.504 --> 01:41:20.563
Carl.

01:41:20.673 --> 01:41:23.642
Listen, Pete, um-

01:41:26.679 --> 01:41:28.579
You take care of yourself.

01:41:31.050 --> 01:41:33.177
I'll save you a tee time.

01:41:35.621 --> 01:41:38.488
Tom, you did a great job.
I was proud to work with you.

01:41:38.590 --> 01:41:40.490
- Thanks.
- Thanks a lot.

01:41:40.592 --> 01:41:43.925
I'll see you guys. Good careers.

01:41:44.029 --> 01:41:46.554
Take care.

01:41:46.665 --> 01:41:48.792
Do well, guys. See you soon.

01:41:48.901 --> 01:41:51.836
- Hey, Pete.
- Yeah?

01:41:53.205 --> 01:41:55.696
This could be trouble.

01:41:55.808 --> 01:42:00.472
- I'm gonna walk out of the
White House carrying this?

01:42:00.579 --> 01:42:03.548
Thanks, guys.

01:42:04.883 --> 01:42:07.545
- Bye-bye. All the best.
<i>- Hey, Pete!</i>

01:42:07.653 --> 01:42:09.678
You gonna leave
without saying good-bye?

01:42:09.788 --> 01:42:12.222
Well, look who's no longer a rookie.

01:42:12.324 --> 01:42:14.315
Thanks.

01:42:14.426 --> 01:42:16.519
So, how about
a little retirement dinner tonight?

01:42:16.628 --> 01:42:19.392
I can't. I got a date.

01:42:19.498 --> 01:42:22.831
- Something you want to tell me?
- With my wife.

01:42:22.935 --> 01:42:25.028
That's great.

01:42:25.137 --> 01:42:28.129
- Pete.
- See you around campus, Jill.

01:42:28.240 --> 01:42:30.834
- Thanks for everything.
- Pleasure.

01:42:33.846 --> 01:42:36.474
Yeah, I'm gonna miss it.

01:42:36.582 --> 01:42:39.142
